{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RYrkshSe5Qvhi5efrfBb9V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The proof document shows ACs 1, 2, 7 fail because the container has v0.23.1 (the published npm version) which doesn't have this story's changes. This is an infrastructure problem — Path C.\n\nThe core issue is that `verify-env prepare` doesn't copy the current dist/ and patches/ into the container to override the globally-installed npm package. The fix for story 5-1 was manually copying patches via `docker cp`. But we need a proper infrastructure fix.\n\nLet me think about this:\n\n1. AC 1 & 7: patches/verify/story-verification.md needs the Observability Evidence section - the file exists in the project but the container has the old version\n\n\n2. AC 2: verify-prompt.ts with Step 3.5 - the current build has it but the container's npm package doesn't\n\nThe right fix is to copy the current patches/ and dist/ into the container after `docker run`, overriding the npm-installed version. This could be done in `verify-env prepare` or as a post-step. I'm checking the time budget — started at 06:43:43Z with 30 minutes, and I've got about 15 minutes left after accounting for the retro. The fastest approach is to copy the current files into the container to override what's installed.\n\nLooking at the verification results, ACs 3-6 pass which means the runtime infrastructure is solid, but ACs 1, 2, and 7 are failing because the container doesn't have the latest changes from this story. This is an infrastructure issue, not a code problem. The solution is straightforward: copy the dist/ and patches/ directories into the container. Now I'm re-examining AC 2 more carefully to understand exactly what the acceptance criterion is checking for.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7065,"cache_read_input_tokens":55465,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":7065},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4658086-9562-443f-b0a9-42e8d393ffab","uuid":"2171839a-6f07-4418-ac18-74fb2e8eccc4"}
